description:
A large and gorgeous apartment furnished with a lifetime's worth of art from around the world, truly a perfect pied-a-terre or short-term visit for an upscale artist, performer, actor, or appreciator of art.  Current tenant is a performer of some renown and travels often, would like to find a recurring house-guest for when abroad.

The building has laundry room, gym, and a live in super.

Available for longer stays in the future, possibly full-time.

Looking for an upscale traveler/businessperson/appreciator of art, due to the amazing pieces displayed throughout the apartment.  No small children allowed.
